data.description: Welcome, to this appealing 2 bedroom, 1 bath home. It is truly a special Staten Island find in the highly desirable Tottenville neighborhood. The home is found on a quiet, low traffic street surrounded by million dollar homes. Just a few blocks from the beach (no flood insurance required). The home features hardwood floors throughout and vaulted ceiling that gives you that desired spacious feel. The two car driveway in the front and the surprisingly spacious 2500 sq. ft. lot adds to the charm of the property. Why purchase a 2 bedroom condo when you can own this lovely fully detached 2 bedroom home. All it is missing is you!
